<HEAD>Jeers And Cheers For Fired Iran-Contra Scandal Figure</HEAD>
<DATELINE>CUPERTINO, Calif. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Some 300 people turned out to jeer
fired National Security Council aide Oliver North while he urged
